4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners, enabling them to start a career as data scientists in just 16 weeks. The program includes instruction in Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore various algorithms. The course features three classes per week, with a maximum of 12 students per class, and certificates recognized by multiple organizations. No prior experience is needed, and classes are available in English and Spanish. For additional information, visit [4geeksacademy.com](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop